import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = 'frontend'; constructor(private router: Router) {} isLoginPage(): boolean { return this.router.url === '/login'; } }
